Use "make" to compile
raylib is a dependency

--Blockpuzzle--
Commands:
    Move the piece: left and right arrow keys
    Rotate the piece: up arrow key and right SHIFT key
    Drop the piece: down arrow key and SPACE key
    Hold the piece: C key
    Reset the game: F4 key
    Pause: Minimize the window

--Minesweeper--
Commands:
    Left click on the cell to uncover it
    Right click on the covered cell to flag it
    Reset the game: F4 key
Game parameters:
    ./minesweeper <grid width> <grid height> <mines number>
